    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064990/extras/42a207965fa0ba834524297870e68be2.poster.avif?t=1748345108\" width=640 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064990/extras/42a207965fa0ba834524297870e68be2.webm?t=1748345108\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064990/extras/42a207965fa0ba834524297870e68be2.mp4?t=1748345108\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cart To The End is a <strong>First-Person Multiplayer Game</strong> where you must ride all the way to the end avoiding different kinds of obstacles and escaping other players which can kill you and make you suffer. <strong>This game can be quite hard, so good luck and have fun</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Cart To The End you can annoy other players by making them die and restarting their whole progress by <strong>shooting </strong> them, isn't that fun.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064990/extras/794b7d70aa846fe75816df217efdcb8f.poster.avif?t=1748345108\" width=640 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064990/extras/794b7d70aa846fe75816df217efdcb8f.webm?t=1748345108\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064990/extras/794b7d70aa846fe75816df217efdcb8f.mp4?t=1748345108\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Avoid different <strong>obstacles</strong> to stay alive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064990/extras/509114e5d08f92176d2d4702f80156aa.poster.avif?t=1748345108\" width=640 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064990/extras/509114e5d08f92176d2d4702f80156aa.webm?t=1748345108\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064990/extras/509114e5d08f92176d2d4702f80156aa.mp4?t=1748345108\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Up To 20 Players</strong></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Server List</strong></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Proximity Chat</strong></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Can play by yourself or with others</strong></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Annoying Other Players</strong></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Psychological Horror</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>If you haven't been convinced yet, listen to what someone has to say about this game:</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064990/extras/96baecca66575737207c506199c368b3.avif?t=1748345108\" width=100 height=100 /></span> <strong>&quot;Wow this game is just amazing, so much fun with friends, i love it.&quot;</strong></p>",
